data.description: Welcome to this stunning two-story, four-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home nestled in the charming Matthews Village neighborhood of courthouse Estates. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated kitchen boasting new flooring and windows downstairs, complemented by fresh carpet upstairs and a pristine coat of paint throughout. Outside, a new sprinkler system maintains the lush, well-manicured lawn, while a spacious back deck complete with a pergola invites you to enjoy outdoor living at its finest. With the added convenience of a large two-car garage, all set on a generous corner lot, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Call for your showing today!
